  "contentHtml": "This episode is a little different; no news! Michael talks with Yuri Diogenes \n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/yuridiogenes/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/yuridiogenes'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  )      \n                  \n                  and Sarah about the various Azure Security certifications, and Sarah and Yuri \n                  talk about their upcoming study guide for SC-200: Microsoft Security Operations Analyst.\n                  <br><br>\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/248603?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"rss embed thingy\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/248603/\">Study Guide for SC-200: Microsoft Security Opertions Analyst | RSS.com Podcasting</a></iframe>\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/248603/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.microsoftpressstore.com/store/exam-ref-sc-200-microsoft-security-operations-analyst-9780137568291'>Yuri's and Sarah's book: Exam Ref SC-200 Microsoft Security Operations Analyst (Pre-order)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/certifications/exams/sc-200'>Exam SC-200: Microsoft Security Operations Analyst</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/certifications/exams/sc-9